episodes.title: S35 Trailer | Allison after NXIVM
episodes.description: Coming November 10. This is the inside story of Allison Mack — from TV star to NXIVM enforcer to federal prisoner. With exclusive access post-release, this series explores her rise, fall, and what comes next. Is she a victim, a villain, or something far more complicated? Hear episodes early and ad-free by subscribing to CBC True Crime Premium on Apple Podcasts .
